Hi, the same GraphQL query perfectly runs on the GraphQL tool but is not working on the API “<https://api.hubapi.com/collector/graphql>”. What could be the issue? Please help me on this
```query MyQuery {
  CRM {
    contact(
      uniqueIdentifier: "email"
      uniqueIdentifierValue: "***@****.**"
    ) {
      email
      associations {
        ticket_collection__wp_client_portal_display_contact_ticket(
          offset: 0
          orderBy: createdate__desc
          limit: 10
          filter: {}
        ) {
          total
          limit
          offset
          hasMore
          items {
            HubSpot_owner_id
            subject
            source_type
            closed_date
            content
            createdate
            hs_pipeline_stage
            hs_pipeline
            hs_ticket_priority
            hs_object_id
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}```
